name: The Crystal of Tezereum - Galactible™ #26
description:
Holy Gas Wars! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #26, the “Crystal of Tezereum!” This powerful little crystal is extremely rare and is the source of many wars within the Galactiverse! From species to species, wars are waged on those who obtain even the smallest supply. This radioactive crystal provides an unlimited source of gas for those who possess its power! Your mana has been raised by +800,000 bits!

Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations, sound effects, and music made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2022 | galactibles.com
